        "transcript": "Old Behrman, with his red eyes plainly streaming, shouted his contempt and derision for such idiotic imaginings. Vass, he cried, is der people in de world mit der foolishness to die because leafs de drop off from a confounded vine? I haff not heard of such a thing. No, I will not bose as a model for your fool hermit dunderhead. Vy de you allow dot silly pizness to come and der prain of her? Ock dot poor little Miss Johnsy.",
